OL,5, Lawyers acting for the BBC have written
OL,6, to the Investigatory Powers Tribunal   
OL,7, about the alleged police surveillance  
OL,8, of one of its former journalists.      
OL,10,FVincent Kearney worked on Spotlight and
OL,11,Fpresented a programme about the Police 
OL,12,FOmbudsman's Office.                    
OL,14,FMr Kearney believes the Police Service 
OL,15,Fof Northern Ireland (PSNI) may have    
OL,16,Fattempted to identify sources of       
OL,17,Finformation for the programme.         
OL,19,FIt was broadcast in 2011.              
